---
title: Saucy Mushroom Ravioli and Chicken Tenders with Sweet Peas and Crisp Panko Topping
description: Find ultimate comfort from this ravioli recipe that draws heavy inspiration from holiday stuffing. Tender peas and mushrooms are cooked in a rich gravy sauce before coating the ravioli. Our herb and Parmesan-laced buttery panko crumb topping is just the thing to round out this filling and flavourful meal.
